  lead: An interaction of aerosol directly with radiation produce radiative effects. In this report two levels of radiative forcing (or effect) are distinguished:
  term *Aerosol_radiation_interaction
    # extend Glossary

    insert text
      | An interaction of {Glossary.*Aerosol aerosol} directly with radiation produce radiative effects. In this report two levels of {Topics.*Radiative_Forcing radiative forcing} (or effect) are distinguished:

