  name: Earth System sensitivity
  title: Earth System sensitivity
  lead: The equilibrium temperature response of the coupled atmosphere–ocean–cryosphere–vegetation–carbon cycle system to a doubling of the atmospheric CO2 concentration is referred to as Earth System sensiti...
