  name: Ekman pumping
  title: Ekman pumping
  lead: Frictional stress at the surface between two fluids (atmosphere and ocean) or between a fluid and the adjacent solid surface (the Earth’s surface) forces a circulation. When the resulting mass transpo...
  term *Ekman_pumping
